chairman of the board of trimas corporation a publicly traded billion dollar manufacturer of highly engineered precision products for industry mr valenti also serves as chairman and ceo of valenti capital and world capital partners investment firms located in bloomfield hills michigan he is the former president of masco capital corporation and a  year veteran of masco corporation a fortune  manufacturer of homebuilding and home improvement products mr valenti is the former chairman of the investment advisory board of the  billion state of michigan retirement system in his nearly  year participation with the advisory board mr valenti spearheaded the state’s initial investments in venture capital as well as a broad range of alternative investments he served on the harvard business school advisory council and also served on the advisory council at the university of notre dame he serves on the advisory board at the university of michigan business school zelllurie institute mr valenti is one of the  members of the business leaders for michigan and serves as chairman of the business leaders for michigan renaissance venture capital fund mr valenti was crain’s newsmaker of the year for  recipient of the  “spirit of michigan” award presented at the accelerate michigan innovation competition and was presented the  crain’s ma lifetime achievement award previousmaria a thompson nexttimothy wadhams community students alumni business engagement about about zell lurie education programs  funds events news blog news press releases connect with us contact us facebooktwitter sam valenti iii a brilliant memorable largerthanlife character  crains detroit business skip to main content login subscribe connect newsnews container onethis weeks issue breaking news detroit michigan news artsentertainment auto suppliersmanufacturing entrepreneurship fooddrink news container twohealth care jobstalent nonprofits people elections real estate sports business technology awardsawards container onea